Package com.hdmstuttgart.fluffybear.model

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Ingredient
    Class for modelling an ingredient by uid, name and recipes it is contained in.
    Recipe
    Class for modelling an recipe by uid, name, image, cooking time, category (breakfast, lunch, dinner) wether it is vegetarian/vegan, needed ingredients and cooking instructions.
    RecipeIngredient
    Class for modeling the bidirectional relationship between a recipe and its containing ingredients.
